  %h1 wtf?
  %br
  %br
  = "This is one of the few pages containing letters you'll find on our website. We want you to communicate completely without words. We set a good example by using only icons for the navigation on the website."
  %br
  %br
  = "We are two multimedia art students from Austria. One day we thought, that the world could be a better place...and because we are only secretly super heroes, we had to find an inconspicuous way to get rid of some grievous ills. Our first goal is to decrease the amount of empty words, by creating this website ;)"
  %br
  %br
  = "You may still ask yourself \"what the fuck?\" We live in a world where we are swamped with information from various sources. The relevance of these messages is mostly questionable. Especially on social media platforms the spread of word vomit is carried to extremes. This causes the feeling that some people write faster than they think. To counteract this we hope to slow down the process of developing messages by getting you to create them without words."
  %br
  %br
  = "If you still ask yourself \"what the fuck?\"...just try it!"
  %br
  %br
  = "Should you not be able to figure everything out, or you have other questions, or you just want to tell us how brilliant we are, contact us on "
  = link_to "mimimi@piupiu.at", "mailto:mimimi@piupiu.at"
